- Proactively identify hazards and aim to eliminate or implement effective controls to minimise the risk of injury, illness to people or unacceptable impacts on the environment and heritage as far as reasonably practicable;
- Provide systems of work that focus on guiding workers to manage and control critical risk;
- Provide a work environment and fit-for-purpose equipment that minimises the risk to workers so far as is reasonably practicable.
